{"tid":2288483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華晨集團債權銀行已組成債委會","createTime":"2020-11-16T13:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T14:20:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"527c4cf95d1bc23881cf113281f6bef997f66210","tid":2288483,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560312-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560312-20201116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fuz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=46f6a2ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560312-20201116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd941de8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560312-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國華晨汽車集團表示，早前債務違約以及被下調評級，對生產經營造成影響，公司償債能力、未來融資能力都造成較大負面影響，目前正積極與相關債權人協商，同時加大資金籌集力度，爭取妥善化解債務。<br />\n<br />\n刊登在中國債券資訊網的公告顯示，華晨集團已構成債務違約金額合計65億元人民幣，逾期利息合計1.44億元。由於資金緊張，續做授信審批未完成，造成無法償還。<br />\n<br />\n公告提到，今年以來由於債務壓力加大，發生多宗以華晨集團作為被告、涉案金額較大的訴訟案件，並被有關法院採取保全或執行措施查封凍結有關資產或股權。集團說，在遼寧省銀行業協會組織下，相關債權銀行已組成債委會，由光大銀行為主牽頭行。債委會成員對華晨不抽貸，不斷貸。未來華晨將通過加快資產處置，與債委會推進債務重組，多管道籌措資金，但由於生產經營持續虧損，公司現金流仍然非常緊張。<br />\n<br />\n集團又提到，目前未觸發其他債務提前清償條款。對於日前上海證券交易所下發的《監管警示函》，集團將按照要求整改履責，及時履行資訊披露義務。"},{"pid":"898d2a6ef89f20c812b5864d92822fc6e9fd287e","tid":2288483,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"冰山一角"},{"pid":"0578f97ea0303e037266aa6c08e19e688044f551","tid":2288483,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"華晨都收皮即係代表支那車無得玩"},{"pid":"90508cf01494af8b4b48ccd3b18b1201e49110f9","tid":2288483,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"大到不能倒"},{"pid":"ffab4a81e8225f561b0487f98b34d52d0f50bae7","tid":2288483,"uid":24443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0578f97ea0303e037266aa6c08e19e688044f551","tid":2288483,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"華晨都收皮即係代表支那車無得玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"Cap撚哂的錢走姐"},{"pid":"575b21ac48fa061a2b59e19706c80dc981fce9c9","tid":2288483,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffab4a81e8225f561b0487f98b34d52d0f50bae7","tid":2288483,"uid":24443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0578f97ea0303e037266aa6c08e19e688044f551","tid":2288483,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"華晨都收皮即係代表支那車無得玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"Cap撚哂的錢走姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"去美國上巿轉下運<br />\n<br />\n你睇下電車股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bb92c0acb419df0dc13f0a7862604836cd29ee","tid":2288483,"uid":265497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"以前咪代工寶馬係大陸賣，訓係度都賺。<br />\n<br />\n寶馬一走，成檔野即刻收皮"},{"pid":"cb5d86dfc114c560d1557e26d09fdf92bd2d5e1e","tid":2288483,"uid":132486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"支那狗乸係時間做返性奴隸，支那狗做返偷仔<br />\n諗住都開心！"},{"pid":"6971855768a68d1f8d39993b59befc1b1424c37a","tid":2288483,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:12:35.000Z","msg":"著咗草/走資未？"},{"pid":"c45bf4c4db7274092be9e635b01ccb854002abab","tid":2288483,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"527c4cf95d1bc23881cf113281f6bef997f66210","tid":2288483,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560312-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcompone